Sial betullah!

232
00:19:58,989 --> 00:20:02,743
<i>Patutlah En. Cho berhenti</i>
<i>jadi penerbit syarikat kami.</i>

233
00:20:02,826 --> 00:20:03,827
Sebenarnya,

234
00:20:04,953 --> 00:20:06,580
saya nak tamatkan siri ini.

235
00:20:07,206 --> 00:20:09,208
Saya dah penat dan meluat!

236
00:20:09,833 --> 00:20:10,667
Seo Mi-rae.

237
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:13,754
Tolonglah selamatkan saya.

238
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:19,134
<i>Jahanamlah hidup aku.</i>

239
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:26,808
KEHANGATAN HARIAN, DETIK INDAH

240
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:29,478
Seronok, ya?
Kami bagai nak mati, tahu tak?

241
00:20:29,561 --> 00:20:31,146
Betulkah dia suka saya?

242
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,397
Hei, cukuplah!

243
00:20:32,481 --> 00:20:36,276
Tak habis-habis cakap tentang dia.
Awak suka dia sangatkah?

244
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:38,987
Tapi dia tak nak jawab betul-betul.

245
00:20:39,071 --> 00:20:41,698
Tanyalah dia kalau betul dia suka awak.

246
00:20:42,282 --> 00:20:43,992
Jom tanya sekarang.

247
00:20:44,076 --> 00:20:44,910
Sekarang juga?

248
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:52,167
<i>Tanyalah dia kalau betul dia suka awak.</i>

249
00:20:52,668 --> 00:20:54,920
<i>Jom tanya sekarang.</i>

250
00:20:59,174 --> 00:21:02,052
<i>Jom tanya dia. Jomlah. Tanya sajalah.</i>

251
00:21:02,135 --> 00:21:03,262
<i>Nak tanyakah?</i>

252
00:21:03,345 --> 00:21:04,179
<i>Jom tanya.</i>

253
00:21:04,263 --> 00:21:06,098
<i>Tanya sajalah. Nak tanyakah?</i>

254
00:21:06,181 --> 00:21:07,724
<i>Jom tanya dia.</i>

255
00:21:07,808 --> 00:21:09,351
<i>Tanyalah dia.</i>

256
00:21:24,825 --> 00:21:25,826
<i>Masuk.</i>

257
00:21:27,452 --> 00:21:28,787
Apa? Ini di mana?

258
00:21:34,793 --> 00:21:37,963
Ada apa? Kenapa panggil saya ke bilik?

259
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,883
Di luar ramai pemerhati.

260
00:21:43,010 --> 00:21:43,927
Tak nampak pun.

261
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:49,057
Sebaik keluar, saya dikerumuni.

262
00:21:51,393 --> 00:21:54,563
<i>Bawa bersabar. Fokus pada tujuan datang.</i>

263
00:21:55,063 --> 00:21:56,606
Kenapa pandang begitu?

264
00:21:58,233 --> 00:21:59,401
<i>Tapi betullah…</i>

265
00:22:00,819 --> 00:22:02,904
<i>Dia memang kacak gila.</i>

266
00:22:06,199 --> 00:22:07,743
Saya nak cakap sesuatu…

267
00:22:07,826 --> 00:22:09,369
Awak penyelia, bukan?

268
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:11,788
- Jangan masuk kerja esok.
- Apa?

269
00:22:11,872 --> 00:22:13,123
Berhenti masuk kerja.

270
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:18,253
Awak pecat saya?

271
00:22:18,337 --> 00:22:22,049
Boleh dikatakan begitu.
Saya tak bercinta dengan pekerja saya.

272
00:22:23,091 --> 00:22:24,676
Kalau kita nak bercinta,

273
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:26,845
saya perlu pecat awak.

274
00:22:30,098 --> 00:22:32,059
Dia tak tahu akta kerjakah?

275
00:22:32,976 --> 00:22:34,686
Kenapa dia biadab sangat?

276
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:36,271
Nak cakap apa?

277
00:22:38,774 --> 00:22:42,944
Selama ini, mesti semua gadis setuju
nak keluar dengan awak,

278
00:22:43,612 --> 00:22:45,155
tapi saya bukan begitu.

279
00:22:45,238 --> 00:22:47,407
- Jadi?
- Tunjukkan usaha.

280
00:22:47,491 --> 00:22:49,159
Bersungguhlah sikit.

281
00:23:00,754 --> 00:23:02,964
Awak lebih menarik daripada jangkaan.

282
00:23:04,549 --> 00:23:07,761
Maksudnya, awak nak saya pikat awak?

283
00:23:08,428 --> 00:23:11,348
Ya, pikatlah saya.
Tunjukkan caranya sekarang!

284
00:23:11,431 --> 00:23:13,350
Cepat. Kita tak ada banyak masa.

285
00:23:13,433 --> 00:23:15,102
Saya tak jadi pecat awak.

286
00:23:15,185 --> 00:23:18,146
Mana boleh! Bukankah awak ajak bercinta?

287
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:22,025
Saya nak perhatikan awak dulu.

288
00:23:22,943 --> 00:23:24,820
Janganlah! Saya nak cepat.

289
00:23:25,612 --> 00:23:26,613
<i>Ya, En. Choi.</i>

290
00:23:27,781 --> 00:23:28,907
Choi.

291
00:23:33,912 --> 00:23:36,623
- Tugaskan dia ke pejabat setiausaha.
<i>- Ya, tuan.</i>

292
00:23:36,706 --> 00:23:37,541
Apa hal pula?

293
00:23:52,347 --> 00:23:54,015
- Awak tak nak pergi?
- Apa?

294
00:23:54,099 --> 00:23:55,851
Saya dah habis cakap. Pergi.

295
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:59,479
Apa yang…

296
00:24:32,637 --> 00:24:34,723
Saya nak kenalkan diri saya.

297
00:24:34,806 --> 00:24:36,308
Saya ketua setiausaha,

298
00:24:36,391 --> 00:24:39,311
pembantu pengurus besar,
tak kira siang malam.

299
00:24:39,811 --> 00:24:41,855
Nama saya Choi Min-ju.

300
00:24:41,938 --> 00:24:45,025
KETUA SETIAUSAHA
CHOI MIN-JU

301
00:24:45,108 --> 00:24:46,943
Saya pasti awak tahu,

302
00:24:47,527 --> 00:24:51,406
pejabat setiausaha Kumpulan SY
ialah jabatan yang mencabar.

303
00:24:52,324 --> 00:24:54,701
Walaupun awak masuk ikut pintu belakang,

304
00:24:54,784 --> 00:24:58,705
En. Choi tetap suruh ikut protokol asas,
jadi dia minta saya

305
00:24:59,206 --> 00:25:01,875
jalankan temu duga kerja yang ringkas.

306
00:25:02,375 --> 00:25:04,294
Temu duga? Temu duga saya?

307
00:25:04,377 --> 00:25:07,380
Ya. Sila jawab dengan jujur.

308
00:25:07,464 --> 00:25:08,965
Makanan kegemaran?

309
00:25:09,049 --> 00:25:09,883
Makanan?

310
00:25:11,760 --> 00:25:15,514
Saya suka daging lembu dan babi.

311
00:25:15,597 --> 00:25:16,556
LEMBU, BABI

312
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:20,060
Saya suka semua jenis daging.

313
00:25:20,143 --> 00:25:21,019
Apa hobi awak?

314
00:25:21,102 --> 00:25:25,732
Awak suka janji temu bagaimana?
Awak nak melancong ke mana?

315
00:25:29,027 --> 00:25:31,738
- Betulkah ini temu duga?
- Ciri lelaki idaman?

316
00:25:32,864 --> 00:25:36,034
Kenapa dia tak tanya sendiri?
Suruh orang tanya pula.

317
00:25:36,117 --> 00:25:37,744
Sebentar.

318
00:25:40,497 --> 00:25:41,957
Ya, En. Choi?

319
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,083
Ya.

320
00:25:43,166 --> 00:25:44,042
Okey.

321
00:25:44,668 --> 00:25:46,836
Alahan dan saiz kasut.

322
00:25:47,337 --> 00:25:48,964
Saya akan tanya sekarang.

323
00:25:49,464 --> 00:25:51,383
Ya, nanti saya sampai.

324
00:25:52,217 --> 00:25:53,051
En. Ko!

325
00:25:53,134 --> 00:25:54,094
EN. KO
PEMANDU

326
00:25:54,177 --> 00:25:57,222
- Kenapa belum jalan?
- Ada kereta halang kita.

327
00:25:58,807 --> 00:26:01,101
En. Choi suruh kita cepat.

328
00:26:01,184 --> 00:26:03,019
Tak nak jalan, ya?

329
00:26:04,813 --> 00:26:06,731
Hei! Maafkan saya.

330
00:26:06,815 --> 00:26:08,483
Aku pun dah lama tak gaduh.

331
00:26:08,984 --> 00:26:10,777
Hei! Bodoh!

332
00:26:13,405 --> 00:26:15,282
Biar saya uruskan.

333
00:26:17,784 --> 00:26:18,618
Hoi!

334
00:26:19,578 --> 00:26:22,581
Alamak, dia nak buat apa?

335
00:26:22,664 --> 00:26:23,957
- Tak apa.
- Hei!

336
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,750
En. Ko bukan orang biasa.

337
00:26:31,506 --> 00:26:32,716
Siap.

338
00:26:38,471 --> 00:26:41,600
<i>Perlukah mereka masukkan</i>
<i>babak daripada komik?</i>

339
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:48,523
Cik Seo, En. Choi nak jumpa.

340
00:26:50,317 --> 00:26:51,318
Sila ikut sini.

341
00:26:56,364 --> 00:26:57,866
En. Choi

342
00:26:58,575 --> 00:27:00,660
tak suka orang ketuk dua kali.

343
00:27:01,286 --> 00:27:03,455
Lain kali, kalau nak ketuk pintu,

344
00:27:03,538 --> 00:27:06,958
ketuk perlahan sekali pun dah cukup.

345
00:27:09,419 --> 00:27:11,254
- Mengarut betul.
- Apa?

346
00:27:12,922 --> 00:27:14,215
Tak ada apa-apa.

347
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:16,885
Apa kata awak cuba? Ketuk perlahan.

348
00:27:16,968 --> 00:27:18,094
Ketuk perlahan.

349
00:27:24,225 --> 00:27:25,310
Masuk.

350
00:27:25,852 --> 00:27:26,686
Silakan masuk.

351
00:27:26,770 --> 00:27:29,939
Sebenarnya, awak ketuk kuat sangat tadi.

352
00:27:32,984 --> 00:27:36,112
Merimaskan betul.
Sama macam perangainya dalam komik.

353
00:27:56,675 --> 00:27:57,884
Apa semua ini?

354
00:27:59,511 --> 00:28:00,345
Bunga.

355
00:28:01,429 --> 00:28:03,306
Kunci memenangi hati wanita.

356
00:28:06,351 --> 00:28:08,770
Hei! Susah-susah saja.

357
00:28:11,648 --> 00:28:12,732
Beginilah.

358
00:28:13,525 --> 00:28:18,196
Saya nak pikat awak, tapi hormatlah sikit.
Janganlah "hei-hei" orang.

359
00:28:26,037 --> 00:28:27,455
Macam mana? Suka tak?

360
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:30,709
Bolehlah.

361
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:33,294
Cerewetnya.

362
00:28:39,426 --> 00:28:41,344
Nak buat apa selepas ini?

363
00:28:42,095 --> 00:28:43,805
Mesti ada langkah seterusnya.

364
00:28:43,888 --> 00:28:45,640
Awak dah aturkan, bukan?

365
00:28:50,478 --> 00:28:52,522
Tak tahu malu betul.

366
00:28:54,858 --> 00:28:56,192
Tak ada janji temukah?

367
00:28:57,277 --> 00:28:59,028
Mari ikut saya.

368
00:29:06,745 --> 00:29:07,579
Ini tak cukup.

369
00:29:08,663 --> 00:29:09,664
Apa?

370
00:29:10,165 --> 00:29:13,084
Ini tak cukup!
Macam mana nak puaskan hati pemba…

371
00:29:13,168 --> 00:29:16,004
Tak, awak rasa ini boleh
puaskan hati saya?

372
00:29:16,588 --> 00:29:17,839
Apa maksud awak?

373
00:29:18,423 --> 00:29:19,674
Ini baru sedikit.

374
00:29:42,614 --> 00:29:44,699
Makan dulu sebelum janji temu kita.

375
00:29:45,366 --> 00:29:46,242
Cuba rasa.

376
00:29:53,416 --> 00:29:55,919
<i>Sebiji macam makanan betul!</i>

377
00:29:57,128 --> 00:29:57,962
Biar betul.

378
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:15,647
Betulkah saya terhutang nyawa
kepada wanita macam dia?

379
00:30:22,362 --> 00:30:24,113
Tiba-tiba nak membeli-belah?

380
00:30:25,532 --> 00:30:26,366
Awak…

381
00:30:27,826 --> 00:30:31,746
Saya perlu jaga status.
Kita tak boleh dating tanpa singgah sini.

382
00:30:32,705 --> 00:30:33,832
Seronoknya!

383
00:30:44,300 --> 00:30:45,134
Apa lagi?

384
00:30:45,635 --> 00:30:46,886
Cubalah baju.

385
00:30:57,772 --> 00:30:58,606
Wah.

386
00:30:58,690 --> 00:30:59,816
<i>Anda ingin cuba?</i>

387
00:30:59,899 --> 00:31:00,733
YA

388
00:31:22,171 --> 00:31:23,214
Awak suka tak?

389
00:31:37,645 --> 00:31:41,190
Kenapa awak sewa seluruh kolam
kalau awak tak nak berenang?

390
00:31:41,274 --> 00:31:43,067
Kenapa? Awak tak suka?

391
00:31:43,985 --> 00:31:45,111
Boleh tahanlah.

392
00:31:52,327 --> 00:31:53,328
Seo Mi-rae.

393
00:32:03,129 --> 00:32:05,048
Cantik tak? Awak suka?

394
00:32:08,551 --> 00:32:09,719
Tak tahulah.

395
00:32:10,345 --> 00:32:12,180
Saya rasa saya mungkin suka.

396
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,541
Awak lambat.

397
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,888
<i>Barulah aku faham.</i>

398
00:32:55,181 --> 00:32:56,015
<i>Ini…</i>

399
00:32:56,975 --> 00:32:58,393
<i>bukan klise tapi…</i>

400
00:33:01,104 --> 00:33:03,398
Cik Yun! Buka pintu!

401
00:33:04,941 --> 00:33:06,275
Ini baru pukul berapa?

402
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:08,236
Cik Yun, saya dah tahu.

403
00:33:08,319 --> 00:33:09,988
- Saya ada idea!
- Idea apa?

404
00:33:10,655 --> 00:33:12,699
Saya ada idea untuk Choi Si-woo.

405
00:33:12,782 --> 00:33:13,700
Apa?

406
00:33:14,325 --> 00:33:16,244
Ingat balik dari awal.

407
00:33:16,327 --> 00:33:17,161
Dari awal?

408
00:33:17,245 --> 00:33:21,249
Awak kata komik ini boleh terkenal
kerana rupa Si-woo yang kacak.

409
00:33:21,332 --> 00:33:22,166
Ya.

410
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:25,795
Lagipun, dia kaya-raya
dan boleh penuhi semua fantasi.

411
00:33:25,878 --> 00:33:29,340
Tapi awak kata orang tak suka
sebab itu klise sangat.

412
00:33:29,424 --> 00:33:31,009
Tak, saya salah.

413
00:33:31,592 --> 00:33:35,430
- Awak salah?
- Choi Si-woo bukan klise.

414
00:33:35,513 --> 00:33:36,556
Dia klasik.

415
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:39,976
Inilah takrif klasik
yang pembaca wanita mahukan.

416
00:33:40,059 --> 00:33:42,437
Wanita betul-betul suka <i>DYPD</i>

417
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:44,856
kerana mereka boleh lupakan realiti,

418
00:33:44,939 --> 00:33:49,694
tapi dialog Si-woo yang klise
buat mereka rasa nak muntah.

419
00:33:50,278 --> 00:33:51,237
Apa idea awak?

420
00:33:51,863 --> 00:33:53,406
Ini yang kita boleh buat.

421
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:57,994
Mari tunjukkan kisah cinta
pewaris harta yang wanita idamkan.

422
00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:03,624
Kita mula dengan pusat beli-belah.

423
00:34:03,708 --> 00:34:04,917
- Ya?
- Aras mewah.

424
00:34:05,001 --> 00:34:05,835
Aras mewah?

425
00:34:08,171 --> 00:34:12,300
Apabila Si-woo tiba-tiba gugup,
hati saya berdebar-debar…

426
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,218
Saya andaikan saja.

427
00:34:14,302 --> 00:34:16,220
- Tunjuk perut sikit?
- So-yeong.

428
00:34:16,304 --> 00:34:18,806
Guna warna-warna gelap di sini.

429
00:34:18,890 --> 00:34:19,724
Okey.

430
00:34:19,807 --> 00:34:20,975
- Cincin.
- Cincin?

431
00:34:21,059 --> 00:34:23,144
- Batunya kecil.
- Besarkan lagi?

432
00:34:23,227 --> 00:34:25,229
Paling minimum, sebesar ini.

433
00:34:25,313 --> 00:34:26,689
Dengar? Nanti saya buat.

434
00:34:26,773 --> 00:34:29,442
Si-woo pegang tangannya
dan tarik dia pergi.

435
00:34:29,525 --> 00:34:31,152
Eun Na-ra pasti jatuh hati.

436
00:34:31,235 --> 00:34:33,321
Habis cerita. Klasik.

437
00:34:40,912 --> 00:34:42,622
BERSINARLAH UNTUKKU, EUN NA-RA

438
00:35:07,688 --> 00:35:09,941
- Nak beli kopi?
- Ya.

439
00:35:10,024 --> 00:35:11,692
Latte ais satu.

440
00:35:11,776 --> 00:35:14,362
Latte ais satu, 5,000 won.

441
00:35:26,499 --> 00:35:29,001
Lewat baliklah kita,
setiap kali nak kejar tarikh akhir.

442
00:35:30,753 --> 00:35:31,587
Nampaknya.

443
00:35:37,218 --> 00:35:38,427
Saya bukan sengaja.

444
00:35:39,512 --> 00:35:42,390
Itu ayat kalau awak terlanggar
kereta orang.

445
00:35:43,474 --> 00:35:45,059
Saya tahu awak marah saya.

446
00:35:46,144 --> 00:35:48,396
- Tak marah pun.
<i>- Pintu dibuka.</i>

447
00:35:56,904 --> 00:35:59,907
Itu tabiat awak, ya?
Pura-pura buat tak kisah?

448
00:36:01,826 --> 00:36:03,661
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

449
00:36:04,328 --> 00:36:07,748
Macamlah orang tak tahu.
Awak tak pandai buat muka selamba.

450
00:36:10,293 --> 00:36:11,544
- Betulkah?
- Ya.

451
00:36:12,128 --> 00:36:14,755
<i>Kalau dah tahu, kenapa tanya, bodoh?</i>

452
00:36:18,801 --> 00:36:22,471
- Mesti awak pun lambat lagi nak balik.
- Saya?

453
00:36:22,555 --> 00:36:25,057
Ya, awak beli dua kopi.

454
00:36:26,893 --> 00:36:30,396
Saya cuma takut kafe tutup.
Saya nak minum satu semasa balik.

455
00:36:30,479 --> 00:36:32,231
Tak sedaplah kalau ais cair.

456
00:36:32,315 --> 00:36:35,318
Saya tahu. Saya nak balik sebelum cair.

457
00:36:36,861 --> 00:36:38,446
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

458
00:36:40,615 --> 00:36:41,532
Saya pun.

459
00:37:04,055 --> 00:37:05,264
1 MESEJ

460
00:37:05,348 --> 00:37:06,682
Tak guna.

461
00:37:17,735 --> 00:37:18,653
Tak guna.

462
00:37:19,779 --> 00:37:21,697
Teruk betullah!

463
00:37:24,825 --> 00:37:27,078
Jangan membebel kepada Cik Yun.

464
00:37:29,038 --> 00:37:30,373
Jangan mesej dia.

465
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,090
Cepatlah!

466
00:37:43,552 --> 00:37:44,553
YUN SONG
&lt;DYPD&gt; E110

467
00:37:48,683 --> 00:37:49,600
Nasib baik.

468
00:38:01,362 --> 00:38:03,072
<i>Sepatutnya dah keluar…</i>

469
