586
00:49:41,269 --> 00:49:43,814
<i>Ada 899 watak lagi.</i>

587
00:49:43,897 --> 00:49:46,066
Awak yakin Si-woo yang terbaik?

588
00:49:46,817 --> 00:49:50,946
<i>Kalau awak bazirkan langganan,</i>
<i>nanti awak menyesal pula.</i>

589
